    "honesty": "This axis is orthogonal to docking: a drug can dock well and still hit a protein this cancer does not depend on. A gene being a dependency does NOT mean a given drug engages it in the mutant pocket; that is what the docking Delta measures. The two are reported side by side on purpose."
